{"tid":2213499,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"FinCEN外洩文件：匯豐銀行合規報表隱藏的騙局贓款","createTime":"2020-09-22T14:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T00:33:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b51330951894ec7130e08ce77239708e3eef7591","tid":2213499,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/986B/production/_113791093__113788573_tv062671937.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fcpsprodpb%2F986B%2Fproduction%2F_113791093__113788573_tv062671937.jpg&h=39f554f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一批外洩的美國財政部金融犯罪執法網絡（FinCEN）合規報表顯示，英國匯豐銀行（HSBC）明知有客戶涉嫌經營龐氏騙局，仍然為其提供服務，把數千萬美元贓款從英國和美國匯至香港。<br />\n<br />\n美國BuzzFeed新聞網最先接獲這批文件，繼而經由國際調查記者同盟（ICIJ）與包括BBC在內的國際記者團分享。全球400名記者參與了這次調查報道。<br />\n<br />\nBBC電視時事欄目《廣角鏡》（Panorama）代表BBC參與這次調查。最先接觸文件的BuzzFeed記者安東尼&middot;科米爾（Anthony Cormier）向BBC講述了調查經過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/business-54237429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fbusiness-54237429&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I24mB5A%2F6U2CfHiGB6dLXW7A%3D&h=4bff0ba0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fbusiness-54237429&h=42856112\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/business-54237429</a>"},{"pid":"0f7a9790eb96d5fd0d0f046ceb6053906d8f1c51","tid":2213499,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6203f69ba5234e7fd612b22a4a94548c649256","tid":2213499,"uid":45936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:53:05.000Z","msg":"5號仔變5蚊仔不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ag